Sorgu: DECLARE @TableSipGroup TABLE (  [Rkod] int,[RKod_Tanim] varchar (150) ,[Bedinx] int,[Beden] varchar (8) ,[skod] varchar (15) ,[SKod_Tanim] varchar (50) ,[Miktar] numeric (32,6) ,[Birim] varchar (10) ,[StokFiyat] numeric (38,7) ,[Fiyat] numeric (21,6) ,[ParaCinsi] varchar (2) ,[iskontoTut] numeric (32,6) ,[kdvoran] numeric (21,6) ,[Kdv_Tutar] numeric (32,6) ,[Otv_Tutar] numeric (32,6) ,[Tutar] numeric (32,6) ,[Kapora] numeric (38,6)  ); insert INTO @TableSipGroup Select  h.Rkod , rnk.Tanim as RKod_Tanim , h.Bedkod as Bedinx , Bdn.Beden as Beden , h.skod , st.Tanim as SKod_Tanim , (case k.SatTip when 1 then -1 when 5 then -1 else 1 end)*(h.Miktar) as Miktar,  h.Birim  as Birim, stokfiyat.sonuc as StokFiyat, tutar.Fiyat as Fiyat ,'TL' as ParaCinsi , (case k.SatTip when 1 then -1 when 5 then -1 else 1 end)*tutar.iskTutar as iskontoTut  , h.kdvoran  , (case k.SatTip when 1 then -1 when 5 then -1 else 1 end)*tutar.kdvTutar as Kdv_Tutar  , (case k.SatTip when 1 then -1 when 5 then -1 else 1 end)*tutar.otvTutar as Otv_Tutar  , (case k.SatTip when 1 then -1 when 5 then -1 else 1 end)*tutar.NetTutar as Tutar  , (case when (k.SatTip=2) or (k.SatTip=5) then (Select Sum(kapora.sonuc)*(case when (k.SatTip=2) then 1 else -1 end) from Odeme_Tipi oti CROSS APPLY dbo.kg_ifn_DovHes(oti.ParaCinsi, 'TL', oti.OdTar, oti.Tutar) kapora where oti.SatNo=k.SatNo) else 0 end) as Kapora  From PosSat_Kay k Join PosSat_Har h on k.SatNo=h.SatNo   Left Outer Join StokKart st on (st.Skod=h.skod)   Left Outer Join Musteri_Kart cr On (cr.MKod=k.MusKod)  Cross Apply Dbo.kg_ifn_PSFindiskOran(h.SatNo) as iskoran  Cross Apply dbo.kg_ifn_GetOdemeTip(k.SatNo) as odemetip  Cross Apply dbo.kg_ifn_GetAlSatFiy(h.skod,h.rkod,h.bedkod,'','a',getdate(),h.ParaCinsi,k.Location,'S') as alsat  Cross Apply dbo.kg_ifn_DovHes(h.ParaCinsi, 'TL', k.SatTar, (alsat.sonuc)) as stokfiyat    LEFT JOIN PosSatTutar tutar on tutar.FisNo=k.SatNo and tutar.FisHarinx=h.SatHarinx and tutar.LineType='S' and tutar.ParaCinsi='TL'  Left Outer Join dbo.P_RNK_Tip rnk On (rnk.Renk_kod=h.Rkod)  Left Outer Join dbo.P_Beden_D Bdn on (Bdn.Bedinx=h.Bedkod)  Where  (k.SatTar>=cast('04-03-2024 00:00:00.000' as datetime))  AND  (k.SatTar<=cast('10-03-2024 23:59:59.000' as datetime))  AND (k.Location in ('LN001','LN002','LN003','LN004')) AND ((k.SatTip=N'0') or (k.SatTip=N'2')) AND  (isNull(st.Pasif,'')=''); Select * into ##751969204FD54807B6DA6C413D9C4E2B from (Select Top 100 PERCENT  RKod, RKod_Tanim ,  Bedinx, Beden , ma.SKod, SKod_Tanim  , sum(Miktar) as Miktar , Birim , (isnull(sum(Miktar),0)*100/cast('10193' as numeric(21, 6))) as MYuzde  , Sum(StokFiyat) as StokFiyat, Sum(Fiyat) as Fiyat , ma.ParaCinsi , Sum(iskontoTut) as iskontoTut  , Sum(KDV_Tutar) as KDV_Tutar, Sum(OTV_Tutar) as OTV_Tutar, Sum(Tutar) as Tutar , Avg(Kapora) as Kapora  , (isnull(Sum(Tutar),0)*100/cast('4507307.1283' as numeric(21, 6))) as TYuzde  From @TableSipGroup ma  Group By RKod , RKod_Tanim, Bedinx, Beden,ma.SKod, SKod_Tanim, ma.ParaCinsi , Birim) asa; Select CreatedField.*, (Select isnull(dbo.kg_fn_GetStkCMik(CreatedField.[SKod], CreatedField.[RKod], CreatedField.[Bedinx], '', Null, Null, CreatedField.[Birim], '*','*'),0)) as [Stok_Detay_Mevcudu], (Select isnull(dbo.kg_fn_GetStkCMik(CreatedField.[SKod], CreatedField.[RKod], CreatedField.[Bedinx], 'LN001', Null, Null, CreatedField.[Birim], '*','*'),0)) as [LindonMerkez], (Select isnull(dbo.kg_fn_GetStkCMik(CreatedField.[SKod], CreatedField.[RKod], CreatedField.[Bedinx], 'LN002', Null, Null, CreatedField.[Birim], '*','*'),0)) as [Pinarbasi], (Select isnull(dbo.kg_fn_GetStkCMik(CreatedField.[SKod], CreatedField.[RKod], CreatedField.[Bedinx], 'LN004', Null, Null, CreatedField.[Birim], '*','*'),0)) as [Zeki_KUndura], (Select isnull(dbo.kg_fn_GetStkCMik(CreatedField.[SKod], CreatedField.[RKod], CreatedField.[Bedinx], 'LN010', Null, Null, CreatedField.[Birim], '*','*'),0)) as [iade_deposu], (Select isnull(dbo.kg_fn_GetStkCMik(CreatedField.[SKod], CreatedField.[RKod], CreatedField.[Bedinx], 'LN011', Null, Null, CreatedField.[Birim], '*','*'),0)) as [KUSURLU]  into ##D811784C2FEE4B2B8C882F9AFB9846D1 from (Select * from ##751969204FD54807B6DA6C413D9C4E2B) as CreatedField  Select * from ##D811784C2FEE4B2B8C882F9AFB9846D1;
